message.body: Rain/snow mix on sat here...do you know your plans yet?
They're saying up to 8 inches here! I think we'll drive down tomorrow morning, be there early afternoon

Sounds good...dad is out at the farm today so he'll be home. Drive safely! I got in a small accident this am... I hit the back of a lady who stopped suddenly. No one hurt, scrape on her car....just enough to really annoy yourself! Ah well... Be safe.
Oh yeah...we both are...it's just annoying that's all
